  {
   "id": 16,
   "name": "Mira",
   "x": 12,
   "y": 18,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "People1",
    "file": "rtp/People1.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "done"
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "Round and round, Awakened. Descend, remember, descend. One of these cycles, we get out.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 0
       }
      }
     ],
     "else": [
      {
       "type": "conditional",
       "cond": {
        "kind": "quest",
        "id": "awakening",
        "check": "stage",
        "stage": 3
       },
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "\u2026You're back. Of course you are. They always come back \u2014 the System makes sure of it.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You feel it, don't you? You've stood here before. Said these words before. This isn't your first waking, Awakened. It's not anyone's first.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "That's the cycle. The System loops us \u2014 wipes us, wakes us, sends us down again. Most never notice. You're starting to.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "quest",
         "op": "complete",
         "id": "awakening"
        },
        {
         "type": "grantskill",
         "skill": "first_aid"
        },
        {
         "type": "heal",
         "what": "all"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "Hold onto what you bring back. The still place by the square \u2014 the Remembrance \u2014 lets you keep it. Each cycle, remember a little more. That's how we break this. Now go \u2014 descend again.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ],
       "else": [
        {
         "type": "conditional",
         "cond": {
          "kind": "quest",
          "id": "awakening",
          "check": "stage",
          "stage": 2
         },
         "then": [
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Now the hard part, Awakened. There's a fracture below the plaza \u2014 the way DOWN. That's what we do here: we descend.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Down there the System will offer to keep you alive no matter what. Go TETHERED and it won't let you die \u2014 but it watches, and watches, until there's not much 'you' left to watch.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Go UNTETHERED and it lets go. Death is real then. But you stay yourself, and you remember. Lys's brother chose that. \u2026Choose at the fracture. Then come back \u2014 if you come back.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          }
         ],
         "else": [
          {
           "type": "conditional",
           "cond": {
            "kind": "quest",
            "id": "awakening",
            "check": "stage",
            "stage": 1
           },
           "then": [
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "The crystal's right there in the plaza. It only takes a moment \u2014 and it always takes something. Go on.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            }
           ],
           "else": [
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Easy, now. You just Awakened \u2014 the System pulled you up out of the dark, same as everyone in Dawnhearth.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Move with the arrows or the pad; press A to speak and to examine. Your menu holds your Status, Supplies, and the meters that keep you alive.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "It'll offer you the world. Take what you need\u2026 but every favor it does you, it watches a little closer. Mind your Surveillance.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Go on \u2014 touch the crystal in the plaza and let it 'welcome' you properly. Then come back to me.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "quest",
             "op": "stage",
             "id": "awakening",
             "stage": 1
            }
           ]
          }
         ]
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
